{"title":"劝告好心人","authors":["杨某"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"劝告好心人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨某"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右派分子黑心肠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世间竟有中山狼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背后猎人追得紧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇尾乞怜泪汪汪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仁人君子太慈祥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开书袋把狼藏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎人过后狼性露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张牙舞爪更猖狂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"善恶好歹要分详，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追击右派要顽强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决把它打下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不获全胜不收场！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载北京大学D．D．T墙报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}